Menggabungkan Tabel Secara Langsung - Cross Straight

1. show tables;
2. DESCRIBE products;



liat pake SELECT * FROM customers;

SELECT *
FROM tabel1
CROSS JOIN tabel2;

=============================

SELECT *
FROM tabel1, tabel2;

========================================

menggabungkan dua tabel dengan menambahkan kondisi tertentu. :

SELECT *
FROM tabel1
INNER JOIN tabel2
ON tabel1.kolom_kunci = tabel2.kolom_kunci;

=====================================
